n></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26p=
x; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">A departure from Boeing&#8217;s engineer-CEOs of ol=
d, McNerney was financialization personified. Harvard Business School, Proc=
ter &amp; Gamble, McKinsey, General Electric, 3M, then, in 2005, Boeing.&#1=
60;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26=
px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>&#8220;All of us have gotten religion,&#8221=
; McNerney preached, &#8220;Every 25 years a big moonshot &#8230; and then =
produce a 707 or a 787 &#8211; that&#8217;s the wrong way to pursue this bu=
siness. </span><strong>The more-for-less world will not let you pursue moon=
