160;</span></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-he=
ight: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Ambitions crumbled like 737 MAXes as mecha=
nical engineering gave way to financial engineering. Innovation moved from =
the drafting table and assembly line to the spreadsheet.&#160;</p><p style=
=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0=
 20px 0;">A decade later, we know how that turned out.&#160;</p><p style=3D=
"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20=
px 0;"><span>Trawling through the wreckage of a once-great company, analyst=
s have created a litany of crash reports. My favorites are David Perell&#82=
