ight: 1.16em; margin: 1em 0 0.625em 0; position: relative;"><strong>Stage 1=
a: Adaptive Business Model&#160;</strong></h4><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55=
, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Rockets are=
 an important gate for the business, but when I asked Ian what happens if t=
he launch business is slower than expected, he told me they have other opti=
