e</em></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height:=
 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Because airlines spend so much on planes &#8211=
; because CapEx dominates OpEx &#8211; their model is built around running =
