one day, people, to space.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); fon=
t-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>This is the </s=
pan><strong>tens or hundreds of billions of dollars per year opportunity</s=
trong><span>.&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size=
: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">At this point, it would be =
The Aerospace Company, feasibly worth $1 trillion.&#160;</p><p style=3D"col=
or: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0=
;">To be fair, the plan seems impossibly hard, dependent on a perfectly orc=
hestrated series of technical and commercial achievements that would make R=
ube Goldberg himself dizzy. It will take a very long time, and billions of =
dollars. If it starts working, competitors will strike and incumbents will =
sue.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-hei=
ght: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>It&#8217;s a deeply complex plan, one=
 that should beggar belief. I&#8217;m not saying it&#8217;s likely to work.=
 But I think there </span><em>is</em><span> a real opportunity to rethink a=
ir travel right now, and this is the kind of plan it would take to do it.&#=
160;</span></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-he=
ight: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Just as in software, physical industries e=
xperience platform shifts &#8211; like from the propeller to the jet engine=
 in air travel &#8211; that create the opportunity for generational compani=
es.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-heig=
ht: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Those shifts are just an opportunity, not a =
guarantee. They&#8217;re not even a very good shot; just the little crack n=
eeded to earn the right to try to do something impossibly hard.&#160;</p><p=
 style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margi=
n: 0 0 20px 0;">Then, it&#8217;s up to an entrepreneur with the Wright Stuf=
f.&#160;</p><h3 class=3D"header-with-anchor-widget" style=3D"-moz-appearanc=
