st of what the company hopes will be hundreds or thousands that will climb =
the atmosphere like a ladder and ride the specific impulse curve up to Mach=
 2.7.&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; =
line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Astro Mechanica plans to unveil its=
 engine live at YC Demo day next Wednesday in what has a shot to be one of =
the most memorable demos in the incubator&#8217;s history.&#160;</p><p styl=
e=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 =
